<ActionDescription>
<p>This sample demonstrates an interactive solar panel tilt system built with the SyncfusionÂ® Blazor Diagram component, enabling real-time visualization of system efficiency adjustments based on solar angle and geographic location.</p>

<p>Key features:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Interactive solar panel visualization with adjustable tilt angle</li>
  <li>Real-time efficiency calculations based on sun position and location</li>
  <li>Dynamic gauge display showing system performance metrics</li>
  <li>Regional location selection for observing geographic impact on solar efficiency</li>
  <li>Curved connector representing the sun's path trajectory</li>
</ul>

<p>Users can adjust panel angles through direct rotation or integrated text input, receiving immediate performance feedback through the dynamic efficiency gauge and contextual messages.</p>
</ActionDescription>

